name: Monkey King
description: Wukong Finance is a high security Yield farming DAPP and crypto platform running on the Ethereum Mainnet using the Uniswap Exchange. Offering a safe and secure platform with great APRs and functionalities is Wukong Finance's highest priority. The idea behind this project is to create a safe and secure place for farmers. Besides the regular high APR farms/pools and bushes, Wukong Finance offers fun games and NFT to play and earn! Wukong Finance is a community driven project with its own special perks governance token WUKONG.
